    "Rapha\u00ebl's legacy is that he fused a Marxist dialectic with sociology, political economy, art history, and philosophical aesthetics into a single methodology.": [],
    "Socialist countries ignored his work (except for Poland and Bulgaria) because his theory was not compatible with official Socialist Realism.": [],
